## Iteration Process

| Index | Character | Condition | Output |
| ----- | --------- | --------- | ------ |
| 0     | b         | b != a    | b      |
| 1     | a         | a == a    | skip   |
| 2     | n         | n != a    | bn     |
| 3     | a         | a == a    | skip   |
| 4     | n         | n != a    | bnn    |
| 5     | a         | a == a    | skip   |

